{"tid":1673619,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳雲：加泰集會 中英文不符合 是要誤導民眾 是要用中文來欺壓本土華人嗎","createTime":"2019-10-24T17:54:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T14:02:53.000Z","uid":133680,"like":6,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a4606301fe8cf9b6aa46590f8dc16e195caff0d4","tid":1673619,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T17:54:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10157522281392225&amp;id=589657224\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10157522281392225%26id%3D589657224&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNgvpIPIfgcH1aomtamkqoQA%3D&h=0280c361\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10157522281392225&amp;id=589657224</a><br />\n<br />\n陳雲：我在香港做了幾十年人，在英治時代生活三十幾年，最痛恨的是在政治行動的時候，中英文不符合。這是最殖民主義、最歧視本土華人的政治欺騙。從上世紀八十年代，我就批評英治政府在中英文的不吻合，而且處處用中文欺騙香港華人，但英文確是正正常常。<br />\n這個今晚（星期四）舉辦的加泰人權自由集會，就是中英文不符合。中文是「香港加泰人權自由集會」，是蓄意誤導。加泰在憲政民主的西班牙之內，西班牙在憲政民主的歐盟之內。加泰有人權也有自由，加泰沒有的，是自治州轉為獨立。他們現在要的是獨立，不是人權與自由，也不是民主。今晚的集會就是支持加泰獨立，除此之外別無他途。<br />\n英文呢，正正常常，就是與加泰人團結，也就是stand with Catalonia的意思，認同他們被警察鎮壓而出聲抵抗，與香港人被衙差打的處境相似。<br />\n搞這個活動的人，是要用中文來欺壓本土華人嗎？他們是英文殖民者嗎？<br />\n正如光復香港，時代革命，往往就不敢翻譯為Liberate Hong Kong.  Revolution by our Generation.  前句Liberate Hong Kong, 也是我提倡用的，他們才跟隨，之前他們用Free Hong Kong而已。"},{"pid":"f32fd743f3deab906ae8de88edacfed63fa69771","tid":1673619,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T17:54:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Squwor1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSquwor1.gif&h=dc4a280e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNgvpIPIfgcH1aomtamkqoQA%3D&h=41c8d4a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"8b10f2e12ff3ed0b77236a72b1477302b5206542","tid":1673619,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T17:57:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"105a79f9849e59cdfe172735187c6917585916db","tid":1673619,"uid":34293,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T17:58:28.000Z","msg":"云伯同樓主班水泥隊幾時寂滅  朝早柒入老母閪 夜晚又轉生？"},{"pid":"a9ba87673a395fb3566033ba7ea26f913799e021","tid":1673619,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"105a79f9849e59cdfe172735187c6917585916db","tid":1673619,"uid":34293,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T17:58:28.000Z","msg":"云伯同樓主班水泥隊幾時寂滅  朝早柒入老母閪 夜晚又轉生？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T18:00:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb5dab2dc2ab4f247d70901fbd2f1d1833d1ce01","tid":1673619,"uid":326414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T18:04:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"82aab60714b7e2bb2b05367f0dadb7efcce03704","tid":1673619,"uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fb5dab2dc2ab4f247d70901fbd2f1d1833d1ce01","tid":1673619,"uid":326414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T18:04:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T18:05:28.000Z","msg":"扮睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ff43686c3f202c4b70fcd8c941d1338da837d78","tid":1673619,"uid":282350,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T18:07:31.000Z","msg":"手足想做咪做囉<br />\n各有各睇法，唔聽某一邊講就等於錯咩？<br />\n一百種人有一百種聲音，但和諧共處，咁先係香港嘛"},{"pid":"5573ab253310b4c7be1cf3c10a8f52cdd3d4dbd5","tid":1673619,"uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8ff43686c3f202c4b70fcd8c941d1338da837d78","tid":1673619,"uid":282350,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T18:07:31.000Z","msg":"手足想做咪做囉<br />\n各有各睇法，唔聽某一邊講就等於錯咩？<br />\n一百種人有一百種聲音，但和諧共處，咁先係香港嘛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T18:09:48.000Z","msg":"而家屌緊佢地呃鳩你地，中英文唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff0498409687a9e86efc452a51428ef4c48e398b","tid":1673619,"uid":282350,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5573ab253310b4c7be1cf3c10a8f52cdd3d4dbd5","tid":1673619,"uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8ff43686c3f202c4b70fcd8c941d1338da837d78","tid":1673619,"uid":282350,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T18:07:31.000Z","msg":"手足想做咪做囉<br />\n各有各睇法，唔聽某一邊講就等於錯咩？<br />\n一百種人有一百種聲音，但和諧共處，咁先係香港嘛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T18:09:48.000Z","msg":"而家屌緊佢地呃鳩你地，中英文唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T18:13:21.000Z","msg":"不同理解字面意義啫<br />\n我都唔覺得係有支持獨立既意味<br />\nanyway，大家都可以有自己睇法"},{"pid":"db0c40ee73555a476ca6ce0b9aa00783f37e5278","tid":1673619,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T18:19:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afe8f4842f821dda71f67f0e2d6413dff2119b08","tid":1673619,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:48:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/y8NCwF9y/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2Fy8NCwF9y%2Fimage.jpg&h=57512e39&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10e3ad5a08920f666b6359862f6048cc4860db81","tid":1673619,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:49:24.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">陳雲同志跳舞做小丑<br />\n獻唱中央真可愛</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KeT4Nz9yRhY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKeT4Nz9yRhY&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNgvpIPIfgcH1aomtamkqoQA%3D&h=a35f0f88\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KeT4Nz9yRhY</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://upload.cc/i2/sSvkfE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FsSvkfE.jpg&h=e27b4e9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://upload.cc/i2/mFNszE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FmFNszE.jpg&h=d405a43b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f053eb739772de77ff39b9d94bcecd873d47530a","tid":1673619,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:49:54.000Z","msg":"陳雲：我幫梁天琦助選是毓民號令的，我是被動參加<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/07/163009_f02e55e1f1a26523551cb121e5fdbb7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F07%2F163009_f02e55e1f1a26523551cb121e5fdbb7d.jpg&h=2054cc23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SGeGiNuvhZI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSGeGiNuvhZI&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNgvpIPIfgcH1aomtamkqoQA%3D&h=04bb9ec0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SGeGiNuvhZI</a>"},{"pid":"3e13ad9e685cec2ba6c0036694829b730121fafb","tid":1673619,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:50:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n陳雲_民族主義_龍門飄移</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10153933887492225 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwan.chin.75%2Fposts%2F10153933887492225%20&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNgvpIPIfgcH1aomtamkqoQA%3D&h=f7494be2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10153933887492225 </a><br />\n<br />\nWan Chin <br />\n2016年3月10日 &middot; <br />\n<br />\n陳雲： <br />\n<br />\n《香港城邦論》通篇，沒有民族主義理論！我不是什麼文化民族主義或公民民族主義。我提到民族主義的一處，是說中共如何利用民族主義壓迫香港而已。為什麼陳雲的《香港城邦論》沒有提及民族主義理論的呢？因為我是用嚴謹的歷史考察和文化史論證而不採取急躁而不必要的歐洲政治理論。普世價值、民族主義這些毒藥，我認為香港無必要服用。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10155190329132225 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwan.chin.75%2Fposts%2F10155190329132225%20&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNgvpIPIfgcH1aomtamkqoQA%3D&h=ad0cdb8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10155190329132225 </a><br />\n<br />\nWan Chin <br />\n2017年5月7日 12:41 &middot; <br />\n<br />\n陳雲： <br />\n<br />\n我的本土右翼理論&mdash;&mdash;香港城邦論系列，不單止對香港有用，對中國更加有用，是中華重新建國與化解美國控制的理論。故此，勾結美國的某些中共內部勢力及港共，對之又愛又恨。 <br />\n<br />\n愛，是因為陳雲的理論是<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">華夏民族主義</span></strong>。恨，是因為陳雲這套理論，阻止了這群人賣國求榮，走資美國。"},{"pid":"86236877fbccfeb99cbf744b304ed4bf0940d186","tid":1673619,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:51:24.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">陳雲：華人吃麥當勞，白人笑你們白痴。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10155104224532225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwan.chin.75%2Fposts%2F10155104224532225&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNgvpIPIfgcH1aomtamkqoQA%3D&h=b53bd01e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10155104224532225</a><br />\n<br />\n陳雲：近代的華人，被滿清政府的異族統治取消了文化主體和族群主體，不論在大陸、香港、台灣或海外，都是糊糊塗塗地活着，以為否定自己的傳統文化與民族認同之後，總有好的異族主人照顧自己，從大陸的滿清王朝、香港的港英政府、台灣的日治政府、馬來亞舊日的英治政府、美加的白人政府，好多華人都是混日子，自己私下求社會階梯上進，卻不求民族的上進。<br />\n<br />\n一旦世界向右轉，西方返回建國初年的傳統與民族，華人就陷入黑暗的自我否定之中，上天信仰沒有了、《四書五經》淪落了，連民間的忠孝節義與時節風俗以及一手唐餐好菜都丟了，攬着普世價值、多元文化，和身上的幾個錢、幾張文憑，華人小孩吃着麥當勞、壽司與risotto，白人笑你們白痴。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Lse1aaz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLse1aaz.jpg&h=eeeece89&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8f0974c85838432c6ef8b7b5572159d9ac58a89","tid":1673619,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:51:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">盧斯達恥笑陳雲連政府票數補助都拿不到</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10211553240043520&amp;id=1140397154\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10211553240043520%26id%3D1140397154&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNgvpIPIfgcH1aomtamkqoQA%3D&h=41644839\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10211553240043520&amp;id=1140397154</a><br />\n<br />\n那些以為自己做甚麼都行、自己大向左走向右走哂的人，不要在自己狂轟濫炸、絕人生路之後，又裝作可憐高呼：「點解你地要咁對我啊~~~」那令我作嘔。反事都有因果，講到全世界都搭通了天地線但最後得兩萬票、連政府票數補助都拿不到，都是自己惡業種出來的，打死我都沒用，打死我也不會拿到議席的。安心等做官就是了，這也是華夏城邦論的唯一出路。 <br />\n<br />\n為甚麼早前天天說要搞死你、斷絕異己、看來窮凶極惡的人，另一面又在賣小強，抱怨自己「失去」了議席？不說現在已經2017年，梁游尚且是得到過幾天議席的，至於一天都沒擁有過議席的人，怎麼失去呢？講佛偈嗎？既然已經搭通了中共習近平和美帝的天地線，沒有議席又算甚麼？一日攀龍遇明主，到了習近平也搞華夏復興，北上或者在香港這個殖民地做官就是了，又有甚麼所謂？"},{"pid":"672448505b97e5277d00f448d8d7a950fb0acc25","tid":1673619,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:52:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">陳雲facebook留言慘被抽水</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rO317V4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrO317V4.jpg&h=c4f10bbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/28/192308_3d6b0e5e542de4db25ba81d64860b5f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F28%2F192308_3d6b0e5e542de4db25ba81d64860b5f9.jpg&h=1034ee3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m4kHO2w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm4kHO2w.jpg&h=55f1d04f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6f8af612dbad32621b14735ad2e280ba370cf5c","tid":1673619,"uid":179963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:52:56.000Z","msg":"果五個正評嘅on9"},{"pid":"d2ead56cd8a29ceeb0b32f125489eff2d879aea6","tid":1673619,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"105a79f9849e59cdfe172735187c6917585916db","tid":1673619,"uid":34293,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T17:58:28.000Z","msg":"云伯同樓主班水泥隊幾時寂滅  朝早柒入老母閪 夜晚又轉生？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:52:58.000Z","msg":"水泥隊快啲繼續去twitter炸板<br />\n等睇所羅門大大力叫佢哋收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62402f44d88cdd1d4db45270930cb97df3a03a2b","tid":1673619,"uid":265839,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:53:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cWxaLkx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcWxaLkx.jpg&h=47e2e383&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Op8w0y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Op8w0y.jpg&h=4261c4cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n分化? 五毛?"},{"pid":"d9bd85f7366aea460cda636407cbc1f3d2b8d71c","tid":1673619,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:53:31.000Z","msg":"陳云根大逆祭天<br />\n<br />\n呢D就係城邦派和陳雲推崇既華夏文化正宗，莊嚴無比既祭天 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n西褲，牛仔褲，卡其褲，運動褲，涼鞋，波鞋，皮鞋，boots，再套件淘寶古裝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/xCRBhYSGYVU/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FxCRBhYSGYVU%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=9bb55baf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n===========================================================================<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">祭天大典是帝王獨享的特權，亦稱「郊」或「郊祀」。《公羊傳‧僖公三十一年》載：「魯郊何以非禮？天子祭天，諸侯祭土。」注： 「郊者，所以祭天也，天子所祭，莫重於郊。」<br />\n<br />\n陳云根非帝王天子，根本就無資格祭天！僭越天子去祭天係大逆，係古代係當係造反要凌遲誅九族的！<br />\n<br />\n成日講華夏乜乜乜, 又話係乜野民族學者, 絕對係不學無術既神棍政棍！<br />\n<br />\n連乜野人有資格祭天都唔知！</span></span>"},{"pid":"e672c18b19b2f07a7c7c6d67943d91d02081bb43","tid":1673619,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:54:25.000Z","msg":"無待堂反云<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1208200879265655&amp;id=204247792994307&amp;fbt_id=1208200879265655&amp;lul&amp;ref_component=mbasic_photo_permalink_actionbar&amp;_rdr#s_095f4da0efecc5b663fc4aaf4fc2a412\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1208200879265655%26id%3D204247792994307%26fbt_id%3D1208200879265655%26lul%26ref_component%3Dmbasic_photo_permalink_actionbar%26_rdr%23s_095f4da0efecc5b663fc4aaf4fc2a412&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNgvpIPIfgcH1aomtamkqoQA%3D&h=ca8a73be\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1208200879265655&amp;id=204247792994307&amp;fbt_id=1208200879265655&amp;lul&amp;ref_component=mbasic_photo_permalink_actionbar&amp;_rdr#s_095f4da0efecc5b663fc4aaf4fc2a412</a><br />\n<br />\n在選舉前已想把你除了，授意各種手套做事。另一邊又稱你「賢弟」，陳雲是一個心術不正、表裡不一的人。<br />\n<br />\n有獨立意識的寄物（例如組織，政黨，輿論領袖），陳雲就無法向中國推銷他的執政藍圖。雖然過去這幾年陳雲一直等，一直等皇帝用他的公車上書，但中國始終沒回應，而且中國政府的在香港的激進統治（例如銅鑼灣書店事件），早已令陳雲的基本法至上主義破產。陳雲在網上圍爐已久，但幸好是低票落敗，否則大害於人間。<br />\n<br />\n本來這些事，我兩三年前就看得到，城邦論最終是要中國主動操作實行，才有意思的本質，我也是近一年明白，但顧著陳雲老人家的面子才不說出來。城邦或許可以弄假成真，我以前是如此天真的。但我昨晚突然知道，原來在報社期間，我的港獨言論、港獨報道已經被他視為競爭，必要除去。<br />\n<br />\n陳雲現在言必稱華夏，仁義道德一大堆，擺出前輩師尊的模樣，但內裡其實是心胸狹窄到不得了，自私自利到極點，這種裝模作樣，令我作嘔，下了那麼多清算復仇的指令，污名都在那些假名假專頁之上，陳雲自己不徐不疾的說不認同搞人生計。我以前不明白陳雲是這樣虛偽可笑的，但敗選之後，氣急敗壞。天人五衰，運用完了，越來越多人會看穿陳雲的真面目。"},{"pid":"7f6d90591720a3f8563ccf4b92b1e4908dcfbd42","tid":1673619,"uid":47309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T08:04:37.000Z","msg":"笑死<br />\n樓上好唔比面d熱狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9cea2119b211f317865d240fd752d7c95e0e3ff","tid":1673619,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T14:02:53.000Z","msg":"駁唔到"}]}